; A. Description
;    A list of commands here configures SCU and generates an internal soft reset.
;
; B. Preparation
;    N/A
;
; C. Prerequisite Example (abov_example_config.h)
;    N/A
;
; For more information, read a user's manual of the target device carefully.
;
; SCU
; 1. RESET      : [ N/A ]
;
; SCU
sendln 'cm scu'
mpause 30
sendln 'rsten s en'
mpause 30
sendln 'reset'
